title: Kylie Jenner flaunts TINY waist and impossible curves in racy sportswear but fans spot 'camel toe'
text:

Kylie Jenner pulled on some neon yellow sportswear to do an impromptu photo shoot in her back yard. 
She flaunted her tiny waist in bright yellow shorts and a white crop top. 
But as she hitched up her hotpants to show off her waist, she didn't realised she'd pulled them up a bit too far. 
And fans were quick to point out that she was flashing a "camel toe". Kylie Jenner wore neon yellow sportswear (Photo: Instagram) She flaunted her curves (Photo: Instagram) 
"She has camel toe," one fan commented. 
While others only had praise for the 19 year old's look. 
"You are real goals, Kylie keep slaying," one fan wrote. Fans pointed out her 'camel toe' (Photo: Instagram) 
Last week it looked like Kylie is finally overtaking her big sister Kim Kardashian when it comes to flooding the internet with raunchy snaps. 
The young businesswoman recently launched an Instagram account to promote her latest venture - clothes. 
Not one to ever do things by halves, the cheeky teen shared two pictures of herself flashing her curvy rear to camera on the new page. 
The polaroid-style photos see the star pulling down her jeans to reveal her bum as she poses seductively with her back to camera. 
On her top half, Kylie - who is sporting a platinum blonde wig - is just wearing a red lace bra. Anything Kim can do, Kylie can do better (Photo: Instagram) The star models her new clothing line (Photo: Instagram) 
A second shot shows the reality babe modelling a T-shirt with the same picture printed on it, which is available to buy from her website from Friday. 
Clearly not bothered about the example she's setting to her younger fans, the previous day Kylie was blasted for glamourising smoking. 
Kylie uploaded arty black and white shots of her smoking a roll up to her Instagram on Wednesday, shot by photographer Sasha Samsonova, but her followers were less than impressed. Kylie came under fire from fans after posting this picture (Photo: Instagram) She's not shy about flashing her flesh (Photo: Instagram) 
“Promoting smoking? classy,” wrote one, with another commenter sarcastically saying, “wow ur such a good model to young girls, and most of your fans are young girls what is ur problem? [sic]” 
One concerned fan highlighted not only the dangers of smoking, but the destructive effects it will have on her skin. 
“Smoking is bad… you will end up with skin like a old leather handbag… jus sayin,” they pointed out. Video Loading Click to play Tap to play The video will start in 8 Cancel Play now
